# Brain
##########
brain/api.py â€” may house thought generation or simulation control

âœ… Analysis of brain/api.py

This file is the API endpoint layer for the brain module, implemented with FastAPI. It serves as a simple pulse management interface, not the core thought engine. Here's what it's doing:

ðŸ§  What It Does
| Endpoint        | Method | Function                                       |
| --------------- | ------ | ---------------------------------------------- |
| `/`             | GET    | Health/status check                            |
| `/health`       | GET    | Redundant health check                         |
| `/pulse/inject` | POST   | Injects a pulse into `spine.router`            |
| `/pulse/emit`   | POST   | Emits a pulse and appends it to `spine.ledger` |


